  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Le Terrasse Royal</strong> is an à la carte restaurant serving both local and international dishes with an extensive wine list and sea views from the terrace. It’s open from 8pm – 11pm</p>
<p><strong>I Glicini Restaurant</strong> offers authentic and regional cuisine in an elegant dining room that overlooks the sea. It’s open for breakfast from 7am – 10am and dinner from 7.30pm – 9.30pm. You'll eat dinner here if you're staying half board.</p>
<p><strong>Bellevue</strong> overlooks the Gulf of Naples from its large terrace that’s close to the pool. It offers a casual setting for lunch with grilled specialities, pizzas and salads. It’s open from 12pm – 5pm.</p>
<p><strong>La Marine</strong> is located on the hotel’s private bathing platform and offers drinks and snacks from 10am – 6pm.</p>
<p><strong>Caprice</strong> is an elegant bar where skilled bartenders create sophisticated cocktails that can be enjoyed inside or on the terrace. It’s open between 6pm and 12am.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
