  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is a superb five star hotel right in the centre of Sorrento. It's less than a five-minute walk from Piazza Tasso and has amazing sea view terraces where you absolutely have to have a cocktail during sunset. There's a lovely, traditional decor throughout, great attentive service and excellent food in the restaurant too.</p>]]></listingDescription>
