  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> (Double Rooms) are about 24-30m<span>² and </span>have a balcony. They are located at the front of the hotel with views over the road. They can sleep up to two adults and have air conditioning, TV, minibar, free Wi-Fi, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Sea View Rooms</strong> are about 25-32m<span>² and </span>are located at the back of the hotel with sea views from the balcony. These rooms are available with double or twin beds. They can sleep up to two adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Junior Suites</strong> are about 42m<span>² and </span>sleep up to three people. These rooms have a balcony and are furnished in a fresh and elegant style of light pastel shades. They are available with double or twin beds and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Luxury Suites</strong> are about 50-55m² and have side sea views. The rooms have a spacious terrace and are decorated in fresh pastel tones with tiled floors. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
